{"tid":758833,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"食煙個陣比個細路仔啤撚住","createTime":"2018-07-28T05:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T07:25:28.000Z","uid":75533,"like":70,"dislike":481,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa27c091794d2717ee55f139cacae1261ecf01c","tid":758833,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:28:48.000Z","msg":"話說有野做要去筲箕灣，由東涌搭去筲箕灣都幾係野，咁我搭左咁耐車，一出地鐵站梗係即刻吹返支四，咁我就良好市民黎，好有公民意識唔會做火車頭，我搵個垃圾桶企係則邊食，點知食左半支有個奀挑鬼命既細蚊仔經過望住我，咁我咪望返佢（想知佢望咩），咁樣對峙左幾秒，佢無啦啦同我講：「叔叔，唔好食煙啦，對身體唔好。」<br />\n聽完之後我即刻嬲撚到仆街，我食煙關你撚事咩，即刻兜個煙頭車落佢塊面到，大聲屌柒佢：「關你撚事咩打靶仔，你死我都未死啦，傻閪。」佢即刻喊住敗走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自我感覺幾好，又幫左個識生唔識教既老豆老母教仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3e9cff928196a685f48da38658a45840c9ae87","tid":758833,"uid":75533,"like":50,"dislike":149,"score":-99,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"Ching Ho Ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f215856af04800394c53c923c604fee66b075f","tid":758833,"uid":25085,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"e1d1c6be2668f9a24a44540c7663491020fa7c80","tid":758833,"uid":123920,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"quote":{"pid":"3f3e9cff928196a685f48da38658a45840c9ae87","tid":758833,"uid":75533,"like":50,"dislike":149,"score":-99,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"Ching Ho Ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31675f9666972972a0e23591d70c2fc6dc9b1378","tid":758833,"uid":53798,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"年青一代有救"},{"pid":"c9613e4c99a3bf3f43174